{"tid":1943683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧：七國集團外長均認為中國就疫情發動假消息攻勢","createTime":"2020-03-26T01:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T04:59:48.000Z","uid":125168,"like":540,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"183c917768a1fd128aa6a55cd44891dd4936c9b1","tid":1943683,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T01:43:29.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧：七國集團外長均認為中國就疫情發動假消息攻勢<br />\n49分鐘前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】七國集團外長以視像會議方式開會，討論新型肺炎疫情。美國國務卿蓬佩奧指，與會者都認為中國正就疫情發動假消息攻勢。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧又表示，近期中國官員多次指美國將新型冠狀病毒帶到中國，批評有關言論是瘋狂。他又在記者會中使用「武漢病毒」的字眼，指事件清楚顯示中共對美國人的健康及生活方式構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指，蓬佩奧在會上要求其他國家代表將新型冠狀病毒稱為「武漢病毒」，但各方出現分歧，以致會後未能發出聯合聲明。蓬佩奧在會後記者會未有否認有關報道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=385672\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385672&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4eu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=ca248655\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385672&h=0e4fbf70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=385672</a>"},{"pid":"b653282f8fb7b5b7a41597083cdb385ef6b290d5","tid":1943683,"uid":155095,"like":84,"dislike":6,"score":78,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T01:44:28.000Z","msg":"不過唔認同用「武漢病毒」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5bf3bcab5573500bdd3a34fad0c5662ca872a39","tid":1943683,"uid":125168,"like":157,"dislike":0,"score":157,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T01:44:56.000Z","msg":"品蒽真係講得啱，岀動大量五毛想操控外國輿論只會適得其反令人警覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋要繼續做好文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524a210e80b13b1ea18c9ecb0d1ec02149bf52b7","tid":1943683,"uid":125168,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"b653282f8fb7b5b7a41597083cdb385ef6b290d5","tid":1943683,"uid":155095,"like":84,